705818f-a.title: Brooklyn: Myrtle Avenue - Stanhope Street
705818f-a.text:
Myrtle Ave., at the S.W. corner of Stanhope Street, also showing rear
of buildings facing on Hiimrod Street. The house at right behind the pillar,
is at 140 Stanhope Street. Overhead is the Myrtle Ave. Elevated Line nf
the B.M.T.
May 1929.
Fugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPPODUCED.
